<HEADLINE> Wall St. Stocks Open Higher  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- Stock prices were higher in Tuesday's early
trading.
</P>
<P>
   The Dow Jones Industrial Average was up 27 points in the early
going. Advancing issues on the New York Stock Exchange held a
4-to-3 lead over decliners.
</P>
<P>
   The Nasdaq Composite Index was ahead 32 points and the Standard
&AMP; Poor's 500 Stock Index was up 6 points.
</P>
