<HEADLINE> European Stocks Close Lower  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   LONDON (AP) -- European stocks were dragged lower Tuesday as
technology shares responded to jitters in the United States, and
the telecommunications sector continued to suffer from negative
sentiment.
